# This package commits ONLY its own source (the fetcher + config below). The
# SCI resource files getdata.js downloads (resource.map, resource.001,
# RESOURCE.CFG) and the game's own LICENSE.TXT, the deployed door binary, the
# seeded scummvm.ini/syncscumm.ini, and any logs are runtime content -- never
# committed (the game data is Ryan Slattery's, fetched from his GitHub release,
# not re-hosted here; see getdata.js).
#
# A whitelist rather than a denylist: SCI resource files have no single stable
# naming scheme, so "ignore everything except the tracked source" is robust.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/getdata.js
!/install-xtrn.ini
!/README.md
!/scummvm.example.ini
!/syncscumm.example.ini
